# __PACKAGE_NAME__

Pure TypeScript utilities for EVE Online tooling.

## Installation

```bash
pnpm add __PACKAGE_NAME__
```

## Usage

```ts
import { placeholder } from "__PACKAGE_NAME__";

placeholder();
```

## Development

This package lives in the [node-packages](https://github.com/eve-online-tools/node-packages) monorepo.

```bash
pnpm build
pnpm test
pnpm --filter __PACKAGE_NAME__ typecheck
```

